James Lanphier https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Lanphier 0 James Lanphier (August 31, 1920 – February 11, 1969) was an American actor. He portrayed Saloud in the 1963 film The Pink Panther, and also appeared in films such as Darling Lili (1970) and the television series Peter Gunn (1958–61). He was born in 1920 in Hempstead, New York, and suffered a cerebrovascular accident which proved fatal on February 11, 1969 in Los Angeles, aged 48.
